  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Frame of Mind, you are placed in a world where logic is escaping you. Each area of the game defies reason, requiring you to think outside the box in order to solve the illogical and escape madness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ reality-defying puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world that conforms to your observation </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ minutes of mind-bending gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Mode (Unlock upon completing the Game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by [Sample Text] Studios, a group of 6 in their 2nd year of studying at Media Design School, New Zealand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need help on a puzzle? Want to talk to the devs? Join our [Sample Text] community discord server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CONTROLS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  Mouse To Look</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  'W' 'A' 'S' 'D' To Move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  Space To Jump</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  'ESC' To Pause</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Frame of Mind, you are placed in a world where logic is escaping you. Each area of the game defies reason, requiring you to think outside the box in order to solve the illogical and escape madness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ reality-defying puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world that conforms to your observation </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ minutes of mind-bending gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Mode (Unlock upon completing the Game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by [Sample Text] Studios, a group of 6 in their 2nd year of studying at Media Design School, New Zealand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need help on a puzzle? Want to talk to the devs? Join our [Sample Text] community discord server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CONTROLS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  Mouse To Look</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  'W' 'A' 'S' 'D' To Move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  Space To Jump</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   ⯈  'ESC' To Pause</p>",
